genresAdvancedInfo.name: cryptic black metal
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Cryptic black metal is a subgenre of black metal that emphasizes atmosphere and mysticism. The music is characterized by its use of dissonant and distorted guitars, blast beats, and shrieking vocals. The lyrics often deal with themes of darkness, death, and the occult.
